      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TALK ABOUT TURBO (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (20.14) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. QUICK EDITION (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (20.06) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Warrants plenty of respect. WINGADEE (3) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.3 lengths (20.02) behind Go Forward Blaze at this track. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Well-placed to take this out. SECONDS DOWN (7) looks a top-three hope after a break.",
